snippet.title: Werewolf: The Apocalypse - Earthblood | Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist: https://www.epicgames.com/product/werewolf-the-apocalypse-earthblood/

Can you hear it? The sound of Gaia calling out in pain? Use the gifts of the Garou and harness the power of the wolf to take the fight to Endron, an evil corporation sucking the land dry.

See more Werewolf: The Apocalypse - Earthblood at #NaconConnect on July 7th. 

• With the support of the Creative Europe programme of the European Union
